This paper deals with the problem of universal induction in AGI, which is a topic that falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of genetic programming to search for combinator expressions also involves machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the modification of program representations, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL).
